channel.description:
[center][img]http://i55.tinypic.com/29nzgcx.png[/img]
Hello MoparScape :D Ok so, this is my first project I won't be releasing the source but I will be putting it online once it's up i'll give the moparscape client link ;) Anywho, My goal for this project was to make everyone think it's better then some/most PI/DSPK/Shards which I hope i'm doing good so far. Yes I am Fury_ from rune - server and I update this and the rune - server post every time it's necessary. I'd like to give a HUDGE thanks too all the programmers/developers/graphic masters for this project. I hope you like it :) [i]Suggestions/ratings appreciated[/i] [/center]
[img]http://i55.tinypic.com/z4tv5.png[/img] 90% Bounty Hunter (100% target system) 100% Combat system 95% prayer system 65% skills (Pking server, don't need skilling :p) 75% Modern RS Pking items 100% PKing system Many more ;)
